uploadThumbnail performs R2 upload and DB update without transaction protection.

Impact: Orphaned R2 files if DB update fails. Storage cost accumulation.

Location: packages/content/src/services/content-service.ts:270-304

Fix: Wrap in transaction or add cleanup on failure (like identity-service.ts:66-78):
```typescript
const result = await imageService.processContentThumbnail(...);
try {
  // DB update
} catch (error) {
  // Cleanup R2 on failure
  await r2Service.delete(extractKeyFromUrl(result.url));
  throw error;
}
```

POST /:id/thumbnail endpoint doesn't validate content type matches.

Location: workers/content-api/src/routes/content.ts:218-258

Recommendation: Add validation that thumbnails should only be for VIDEO/AUDIO/WRITTEN, not all content types:
