## Complete Reset Password Flow

Connect the existing skeletal reset-password page to the Auth Worker endpoint for resetting passwords via token.

### Context
- Design doc: design/frontend/AUTH.md — see Password Reset (Phase 1) sequence diagram
- Work packet: design/roadmap/work-packets/frontend/P1-FE-AUTH-001-auth-pages.md — see Reset Password Page spec
- Reference implementation: apps/web/src/routes/(auth)/login/+page.server.ts — working form action pattern with session cookie handling

### Current State
The file apps/web/src/routes/(auth)/reset-password/+page.svelte exists with:
